ol-Allow-Origin 字段是每次回应都必定包含的。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-sp9k0i3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-sp9k0i3","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"附带身份凭证的请求与通配符"}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-dkqmjpb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-dkqmjpb","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在响应附带身份凭证的请求时："}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-bd3pdhz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-bd3pdhz","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230917184338-s26yvgr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-s26yvgr","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230917184338-pzlag4i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-pzlag4i","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了避免恶意网站滥用 Access-Control-Allow-Origin 头部字段来获取用户敏感信息，服务器在设置时不能将其值设为通配符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"*"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。相反，应该将其设置为特定的域，例如：Access-Control-Allow-Origin: "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"https://juejin.cn"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。通过将 Access-Control-Allow-Origin 设置为特定的域，服务器只允许来自指定域的请求进行跨域访问。这样可以限制跨域请求的范围，避免不可信的域获取到用户敏感信息。"}]}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-sgaqlld","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-sgaqlld","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230917184338-uch6tcp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-uch6tcp","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了避免潜在的安全风险，服务器不能将 Access-Control-Allow-Headers 的值设为通配符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"*"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。这是因为不受限制的请求头可能被滥用。相反，应该将其设置为一个包含标头名称的列表，例如：Access-Control-Allow-Headers: X-PINGOTHER, Content-Type。通过将 Access-Control-Allow-Headers 设置为明确的标头名称列表，服务器可以限制哪些自定义请求头是允许的。只有在允许的标头列表中的头部字段才能在跨域请求中被接受。"}]}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-94db1j9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-94db1j9","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230917184338-pftxkp3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-pftxkp3","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了避免潜在的安全风险，服务器不能将 Access-Control-Allow-Methods 的值设为通配符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"*"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。这样做将允许来自任意域的请求使用任意的 HTTP 方法，可能导致滥用行为的发生。相反，应该将其设置为一个特定的请求方法名称列表，例如：Access-Control-Allow-Methods: POST, GET。通过将 Access-Control-Allow-Methods 设置为明确的请求方法列表，服务器可以限制哪些方法是允许的。只有在允许的方法列表中的方法才能在跨域请求中被接受和处理。"}]}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-86vqlad","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-86vqlad","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230917184338-5ftknyu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-5ftknyu","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于附带身份凭证的请求（通常是 Cookie），"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-jpk067k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-jpk067k","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这是因为请求的标头中携带了 Cookie 信息，如果 Access-Control-Allow-Origin 的值为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"*"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，请求将会失败。而将 Access-Control-Allow-Origin 的值设置为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"https://juejin。cn"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，则请求将成功执行。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-zio0mxc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-zio0mxc","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，响应标头中也携带了 Set-Cookie 字段，尝试对 Cookie 进行修改。如果操作失败，将会抛出异常。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-mgd92kp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-mgd92kp","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么本地使用 webpack 进行 dev 开发时，不需要服务器端配置 cors 的情况下访问到线上接口？"}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-fb3pv7v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-fb3pv7v","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你在本地通过 Ajax 或其他方式请求线上接口时，由于浏览器的同源策略，会出现跨域的问题。但是在服务器端并不会出现这个问题。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184338-nym163h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184338-nym163h","updated":"20230917184338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"它是通过 Webpack Dev Server 来实现这个功能。当你在浏览器中发送请求时，请求会先被 Webpack Dev Server 捕获，然后根据你的代理规则将请求转发到目标服务器，目标服务器返回的数据再经由 Webpack Dev Server 转发回浏览器。这样就绕过了浏览器的同源策略限制，使你能够在本地开发环境中访问线上接口。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184354-bw40v4c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230917184354-bw40v4c","updated":"20230917184354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结"}]},{"ID":"20230917184354-1ozmen8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184354-1ozmen8","updated":"20230917184354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"预检请求是在进行跨域资源共享 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"CORS"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 时，由浏览器自动发起的一种 OPTIONS 请求。它的存在是为了保障安全，并允许服务器决定是否允许跨域请求。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184354-6oh8edy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184354-6oh8edy","updated":"20230917184354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"跨域请求是指在浏览器中向不同域名、不同端口或不同协议的资源发送请求。出于安全原因，浏览器默认禁止跨域请求，只允许同源策略。而当网页需要进行跨域请求时，浏览器会自动发送一个预检请求，以确定是否服务器允许实际的跨域请求。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184354-gh34k3r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184354-gh34k3r","updated":"20230917184354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"预检请求中包含了一些额外的头部信息，如 Origin 和 Access-Control-Request-Method 等，用于告知服务器实际请求的方法和来源。服务器收到预检请求后，可以根据这些头部信息，进行验证和授权判断。如果服务器认可该跨域请求，将返回一个包含 Access-Control-Allow-Origin 等头部信息的响应，浏览器才会继续发送实际的跨域请求。"}]},{"ID":"20230917184354-700dqzi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230917184354-700dqzi","updated":"20230917184354"},"Children"